        {
            "title": "「殭屍油輪」將現蹤委內瑞拉 揭示川普已盯上石油運輸的至暗角落",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"via Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"570\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WyJSvwG1Fqj9yTFTxbUZEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7e704bdb0737d43088ba8e8bde261f8a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">via Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 根據船舶追蹤數據，一艘據稱應已於2021年拆解報廢、船齡27年的原油油輪將在本周晚些時候抵達<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:委內瑞拉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/委內瑞拉\">委內瑞拉</a>。這再次表明這個南美國家是如何勉強維持其陷入困境的石油工業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這艘自稱Freesia I的油輪很可能是一艘「殭屍船」，也就是說它實際上是另一艘油輪，而冒用一艘已拆解船隻的身份。這種策略有時會被運輸受制裁石油的船隻採用，以掩蓋其航跡和貨物信息。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"一艘標識為「Freesia I」的油輪顯示將於12月26日抵達委內瑞拉。來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ljGUhel5_PtXI7YqCg4zqA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6499c0f58a906392aa7ceda7c6907aa1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">一艘標識為「Freesia I」的油輪顯示將於12月26日抵達委內瑞拉。來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">委內瑞拉曾經是全球石油大國，但多年來的制裁和投資不足使其石油業遭受重創。但依靠全球船隊中一些最老舊、最不透明的油輪，委內瑞拉的石油出口仍在繼續，主要出口目的地是中國。這些油輪是支撐委內瑞拉經濟和總統尼古拉斯·馬杜羅政府運轉的海上生命線。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7f79547c-b0b7-36de-a241-3b623f17adbf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「委內瑞拉在掩蓋原油來源和所有權方面極為高效，從而成功規避了金融和貿易層面的管制，」Kpler高級風險與合規分析師Dimitris Ampatzidis表示，「這就是為什麼華盛頓越來越多地從純粹的金融措施轉向實際的物理干預。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"564\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KyBr6dr2B5JI0C8zxcs8VA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/103e784c5d10adb13835103e6a9c83f5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Zombie Ship Shows Trump Is Targeting Darkest Corner of Oil Fleet</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
